[fósforo risca]

1089
00:59:09,921 --> 00:59:11,923
[música termina]

1090
00:59:17,136 --> 00:59:18,972
[música de mistério]

1091
00:59:51,087 --> 00:59:52,297
[ecoando] Chegou a hora.

1092
00:59:53,673 --> 00:59:55,675
[música se torna sombria]

1093
01:00:04,934 --> 01:00:06,936
[música aumenta]

1094
01:00:12,817 --> 01:00:14,611
- [acordes dramáticos]
- [grunhidos]

1095
01:00:15,486 --> 01:00:17,989
[acorde distorcido, desacelerado]

1096
01:00:19,365 --> 01:00:21,242
[tique-taque de relógio]

1097
01:00:29,083 --> 01:00:31,085
[música de encerramento]

